{"tid":1291563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"77遊行--政府愈嚴陣以待，我地就更要風平浪靜！","createTime":"2019-07-07T02:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T09:49:11.000Z","uid":275073,"like":248,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"2915cae2d0e7d982c9abcab91ef95e09bf6abdd4","tid":1291563,"uid":275073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:54:44.000Z","msg":"政府愈嚴陣以待，我地就更要風平浪靜！<br />\n<br />\n佢地停晒d商舖，又停售車票，又封閘口！<br />\n<br />\n我地就要俾d商家睇，<br />\n係政府怕事、心虛，<br />\n<br />\n遊行根本 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">好 和 平</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n此上種種蠢行完全係因為政府同班克警<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">錯誤估計、身有屎</span></strong>！"},{"pid":"9cb4a34e7686412a415905c90f68365d2e3c5207","tid":1291563,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c72a8beb81071252a1485742befe24f800f0006","tid":1291563,"uid":199727,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"吹撚到我地暴徒咁樣係咪特登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bac9d93850d040ad604d2d73a0b96ebce157b13","tid":1291563,"uid":54833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"又得D仆街，太陽曬風吹雨打！"},{"pid":"3ad251057c29f3a547241b1eb07bdbef772f4fd7","tid":1291563,"uid":267429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6e5410a2ba7aed318a5ad2789c8d06d8c9d8bfb","tid":1291563,"uid":71216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f27e767fc8f0319cac88e3ea22a3d0f691fe1f2b","tid":1291563,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:15:47.000Z","msg":"be water<br />\n推"},{"pid":"9953a973a80b44423ef73ad892c24015979282ad","tid":1291563,"uid":61596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"482d6e6d06febf38d4a66de5cf53e75d756fe341","tid":1291563,"uid":164374,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"依家<br />\n(1) 警察: 選擇性執法 -&gt; 唔還手, 郁手果個唔會拉, 仲會調返轉拉你<br />\n(2) 傳媒: 選擇性報導 -&gt; 唔還手, 配合(1), 都係比人當你打人, 然後報你暴徒<br />\n(3) 政府: 選擇性讉責 -&gt; 唔還手, 配合(1)+(2), 大條道理讉責暴力<br />\n外國人睇報導, 淨係見倒警察拉示威者,政府讉責示威者, 又要搞一大輪文宣<br />\n<br />\n九品芝麻官就教咗你: 做貪官要奸, 做清官更加要奸<br />\n呢班黑社會藍屍黑警政府中共根撚本無恥到極<br />\n乜到無做, 都係比人抹黑<br />\n唔同佢地鬥無恥, 唔我知點贏呢場戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n對方一路拉人, 一路搵黑社會打傷人, 恐嚇, 我地人越黎越少"},{"pid":"3e23d5897691b3ba65318a094e8f6caafe734c59","tid":1291563,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"大家小心<br />\n今日有暴龍隊出黎開餐"},{"pid":"2dffbaa2942de17ec6dac3137a3b276f662039af","tid":1291563,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ea2eae88872712f65c9da801ee5c671b67df863","tid":1291563,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"今日和平=撚狗"},{"pid":"9bfc4b6bf013d411dfc3c274834a5f5c8c8f417d","tid":1291563,"uid":158876,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢封曬我地唔出現會好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b97fcf743ea7030822170065407fb7dc415be46","tid":1291563,"uid":257961,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9bfc4b6bf013d411dfc3c274834a5f5c8c8f417d","tid":1291563,"uid":158876,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢封曬我地唔出現會好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"轉野餐地點 水鳩佢地一獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c6c5e4ca2c2069b8d3907fe035eb38825cf81e","tid":1291563,"uid":265507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"